SUMMARY:MomCo (Mom Community)
DESCRIPTION:Come join Moms in the same season of life as you!  \nMomCo is designed to connect moms of children 0-grade school.  We provide childcare and interactive programming for your children (ages o-5 years) while you share\, laugh and learn with other moms just like you. Join us in a safe community that encourages and equips. We meet on the 2nd and 4th Monday of each month September – May. 9:00-11:00am.
